      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exemplary 2011 BMW M3 (E92), a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline to deliver immediate throttle response. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring optimal damping rates for both lateral load and high-speed stability. This garage-kept example boasts original paint with impeccable depth and an interior free of any tactile wear. Maintenance is comprehensive, including recent rod bearing prophylaxis and throttle actuator service, ensuring the mechanical longevity of this analog masterpiece.",
